T1  - Competition among markets: The repeal of Rule 390
AU  - Kam, Tai-Kong
AU  - Panchapagesan, Venkatesh
AU  - Weaver, Daniel G.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 27
IS  - 9
SP  - 1711
